TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlString select distinct LPP.PROCESS_PARAMETER_ID as ParamID, LIMI.CORRELATION_STRING as Correlation, LU.IS_ENABLED as UCAEnabled, LU.IMPLEMENTATION_TYPE as UCAImplementationType, LU."NAME" as UCAName, LPV1.PO_NAME as ServiceName, LPP.NAME as ParameterName from lsw_inst_msg_incl limi, lsw_uca lu, LSW_PO_REFERENCE lpr, LSW_PO_DEPENDENCY lpd, LSW_PO_VERSIONS lpv1, lsw_process lp, LSW_PROCESS_PARAMETER lpp where LIMI.ID = ? and LPV1.PO_TYPE = 1 and LPR.TARGET_TYPE = 1 and LIMI.UCA_ID = LU.UCA_ID and LU.PROCESS_REF = LPR.REFERENCE_ID and LPD.TARGET_REF = LPR.REFERENCE_ID and LPV1.PO_ID = LPR.TARGET_ID and LP.VERSION_ID = LPV1.PO_VERSION_ID and LPP.PROCESS_ID = LP.PROCESS_ID
